Reflection
At Automation level, EduSavvy's AI is a parrot — it repeats static content with no adaptation, producing generic quizzes disconnected from Kenyan reality. 
Moving to Augmentation transforms the dynamic: teachers and AI co-create, with human judgment filtering cultural relevance and CBC alignment before any student sees content. 
Outcomes improve because the human's contextual wisdom shapes every interaction. 
At Agency level, a well-configured Autonomous Ranger — like Hesabu Coach — scales this wisdom to thousands of students simultaneously, maintaining Socratic patience and local relevance 24/7. 
Each level multiplies impact: Automation saves time, Augmentation improves quality, Agency compounds both at scale.